<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User Status</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body style="background-color: #f8f9fa; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">

    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="min-height: 100vh;">
        <div class="card text-center shadow p-4" style="max-width: 500px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <!-- Image -->
            <div class="mb-4">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150/FF0000/FFFFFF?text=Account+Blocked" 
                     alt="Account Restricted" 
                     style="width: 150px; height: 150px; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid #ddd;">
            </div>
            
            <div class="card-body">
                <h1 class="text-danger" style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold;">Account Restricted</h1>
                <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 10px;">
                    Your account has been <span style="font-weight: bold;">banned</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">suspended</span>, or <span style="font-weight: bold;">deactivated</span> due to a violation of our terms and conditions.
                </p>
                <p style="color: #555; font-size: 1rem;">If you believe this is a mistake, please contact our support team.</p>
                

                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 1rem;">Contact Support</a>
                <br>
                <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-link mt-3" style="font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none;">SignUp</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
